{"title_page": "Agostinho Mondlane", "text_new": "{{Infobox officeholder\n| name               = Agostinho Mondlane\n| image              =  \n| order              =\n| office             = Minister of Defence\n| term_start         = 14 March 2014\n| term_end           = \n| predecessor        = [[Filipe Nyusi]]\n| successor          = \n| office2            = Deputy Minister of Defence  \n| term_start2        = 17 May 2007 \n| term_end2          = 14 March 2014\n| minister2          = [[Filipe Nyusi]]\n| predecessor2       =  \n| successor2         = \n| office3            = Deputy Minister of Public Works \n| term_start3        = 1994 \n| term_end3          = 2000 \n| president3         = [[Joaquim Chissano]] \n| predecessor3       =  \n| successor3         =  \n| office4            = Deputy Minister of Construction and Water \n| term_start4        = 1990 \n| term_end4          = 1994 \n| president4         = [[Joaquim Chissano]]  \n| predecessor4       =  \n| successor4         =  \n| birth_date         = {{birth date and age|1959|11|21|df=y}}\n| birth_place        = [[Maputo]], [[Portuguese Mozambique]]\n| nationality        = Mozambican\n| spouse             =  \n| party              = [[FRELIMO]] \n| children           =  \n| residence          = \n| alma_mater         = [[Eduardo Mondlane University]] <br> [[University of London]] {{small|([[Diploma|Dip]])}}\n| profession         = [[Economist]]\n| religion           = \n| signature          = \n| signature_alt      = \n| website            =  \n| footnotes          =\n}}\n\n'''Agostinho Mondlane''' (born 21 November 1959) is a Mozambican politician who has served as [[Mozambique]]'s Minister of Defence since 2014.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mdn.gov.mz/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=41:sua-excelencia-vice-ministro-da-defesa-nacional&catid=37:mdn-geral&Itemid=2 |title=Profile: Incumbent Minister of Defense |last1= |first1= |last2= |first2= |date= March 2014|website= |publisher=Minist\u00e9rio